query:
SELECT ef.id as execucaoId, ef.formandoId, f.nome as formandoNome, COUNT(ff.id) as totalFotos
FROM execucao_formando ef
JOIN formandos f ON ef.formandoId = f.id
LEFT JOIN fotos_formando ff ON ff.execucaoFormandoId = ef.id
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Álvaro Pontual%'
GROUP BY ef.id, ef.formandoId, f.nome
